      <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;A simple dialogue which takes place in a restaurant. Part 14 of 14 episodes. It is a good idea to listen many times to each part. This story is available in other languages at &lt;a href="http://www.lingq.com"&gt;LingQ.&lt;/a&gt; You can use these versions to provide a direct translation.&lt;/p&gt;
